text: George Thomas Whitten (26 June 1922 – 28 June 2001) was an Australian politician who represented the South Australian House of Assembly seat of Price for the Labor Party from 1975 to 1985.George Whitten: SA Parliament ==References== Category:Members of the South Australian House of Assembly Category:2001 deaths Category:1922 births Category:Australian Labor Party members of the Parliament of South Australia Category:20th-century Australian politicians
title: George Whitten
